<img src="https://i1.wp.com/www.dunnvineyards.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/kristina.jpg">
<p class="lh-copy measure">
	The youngest in the family, graduated Cal Poly San Luis Obispo with a BS in Wine & Viticulture in 2005. Kristina and Brian Buchanan married in 2010 and now have two young daughters.  Kristina worked at the winery assisting in the winemaking, givng tours and managing the marketing until her children were born. Today she is not involved in the day to day activities of the winery, however she plays a critical role as the mediator in many of challenges associated in family business. 
